These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-4-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, lemonade, milk, tea, water
House: townhouse, wooden, gothic-revival, futuristic, colonial, victorian, art-deco
City: berlin, prague, miami, hannover, paris, san-francisco, rome
 1. the person drinking water is the victorian house##1
 2. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
 3. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
 4. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
 5. the person drinking tea is the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person traveling to prague is the townhouse house##1
 7. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 8. the futuristic house is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
10. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
11. the person drinking tea is in the middle##1
12. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
13. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
14. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
15. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
16. the victorian house is in an odd position##4
17. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
18. the art-deco house is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
19. the person traveling to prague is the person drinking tea##1
20. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | water  | hot-chocolate | iced-tea | tea        | 7up       | lemonade | milk     |
| House   | victorian   | art-deco       | gothic-revival  | townhouse  | futuristic  | wooden   | colonial  |
| City         | rome | paris         | san-francisco  | prague | berlin | hannover  | miami |

