.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-4-2::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: magic-tricks, baking, woodworking, fishing, hiking, drawing, singing
7 different pets are kept: bird, cat, dog, frog, hamster, lizard, mouse
There are 7 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, sprite, tea, juice, mirinda, milk
 1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 2. the owner of the lizard is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 3. the owner of the bird is in an even position##4
 4. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 6. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 7. the owner of the bird is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an odd position##4
 9. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
10. the owner of the frog is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
11. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
12. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
13. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
14. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
15. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an even position##4
16. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
17. the person drinking sprite is in an even position##4
18. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
19. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
20. the owner of the cat is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |       3       |     4      |   5    |       6        |   7    |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | drawing | hiking | woodworking      | baking | fishing | singing |
| Pet         | frog       | hamster | lizard        | cat        | dog    | bird           | mouse  |
| Beverage   | juice | fanta     | iced-tea    | tea | milk    | sprite      | mirinda  |

